description:
This is a 7 minute workout called '7 Minute Stretching - FULL BODY For Mobility, Stress Relief & Active Recovery!' from the channel MrandMrsMuscle.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Here is a highly effective daily stretch routine for the full body that you can add to all of your workouts. This 7 minute stretch workout focuses on releasing tight muscles, increasing flexibility and improving your overall mobility.
You can use this routine when you wake up, after your workouts or even before bed.
